Privacy Policy for SalahMate

1- Information we collect
Data Collected & Purpose:
·	Location: To provide accurate Salat and Iqamah times and detect when you are at a mosque to automatically enable or disable silent mode. 
·	Notifications: To deliver Adhan alerts, reminders, and prayer alarms. 
·	Network Data: Fetches prayer times from our API to ensure accuracy.
Data: This app does not collect, transmit, or share any personal information but third-party services (AdMob) do.
 All prayer times and location data are stored locally on your device.
 
Continuous Location Tracking:The app may track your location in the background to detect mosque visits. This allows automatic silent mode activation when you enter a mosque and deactivation when you leave.
Battery Optimization:Continuous location tracking may increase battery usage. The app is optimized to minimize battery impact while maintaining accurate prayer times and mosque detection.
User Control:
·	You can manually set your location instead of auto-detection. 
·	Notifications and location permissions can be turned off at any time. 
·	All personal data is used solely for prayer functionality and is not shared with third parties. 
Security:All data is stored securely and transmitted via encrypted connections to ensure your privacy.
